        <description><![CDATA[{\rtf1\ansi\deff0
{\b FXPanel for Reaper}\par
\par
Quick-access floating panel for adding your favorite FX to tracks \emdash drag-and-drop layout, per-button images, and a built-in FX browser.\par
\par
{\b Features}\par
\bullet  One-click insertion of VST, VST3, AU and CLAP plugins onto tracks\par
\bullet  Drag-and-drop button layout, freely resizable panel\par
\bullet  Per-button PNG/JPEG thumbnails\par
\bullet  Built-in FX browser with search and folder filtering\par
\bullet  Layout and images persist across REAPER restarts\par
\par
{\b Requirements}\par
ReaImGui extension \emdash install it first via ReaPack: Browse packages > search {\i ReaImGui} > Install > restart REAPER.\par
\par
{\b Support}\par
Free to use. An optional supporter license (available on Gumroad) removes the donation reminder and supports continued development.
}]]></description>
